data.description: HUGE PRICE DROP! Nestled directly between, with views of both lakes, 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath gem is perfection. Acrossstreet from main marina for boating & fishing, close behind Guyenne Park, home of breathtaking sunsets & more fishing on small lake, or short walk to the clubhouse & enjoy golf, tennis, olympic sized pool, restaurant & the BIGGEST BEACH IN LSL! 2300 sq ft & room to grow. Enter into foyer & be in awe of large living space to the left with wood burning fireplace, artsy tv & access to the giant patio w hot tub (stays). To the right, note the storage in the big dining room with artsy TV (stays) & dual access to the shiny kitchen with stainless appliances that opens to the patio over looking a flat yard. Primary bed features sitting area & access to upper balcony to watch the sun rise over the water. Bed 4 can double as office & has access to the rear upper deck (as-is). Bed 3 also accesses the upper balcony. Lower level features theater w equipment & rec area with pool table.
